{
  "texts": [
    "It is implemented on a system using Python with 12GB RAM, 500GB SSD, 2GB Graphics, and i7 Processor.",
    "It achieves an accuracy of 93.58%.",
    "LeNet (LeCun et al. 1998) and AlexNet performs exceptionally well in terms of computing speed.",
    "The concept of dense block is not employed.",
    "Shamrat et al. (2023) proposed a fine-tuned CNN model named AlzheimerNetfor identification of stages of AD and NC class."
  ]
}